
liblangen is a C++ library for generating (regular) languages by means
of finite automata or regular expressions. currently it consists of

	1) a equally distributed DFA generator

planned are:

	2) a RegEx generator

	3) a NFA generator

DEPENCENCIES:

	liblangen only has two dependencies:
	the GNU multiple precision arithmetics library GMP and its C++
	interface (libgmp and libgmpxx).

